history.text: Hello, my name is Tony.
Hello.
Anything going on?  Know any good movies
Know any good movies?
I have been given the synopsis of Batman versus Superman, have you seen that one?
I haven't but I hear its really good.  I am looking forward to seeing it.  Do you know anything about it?
Yes, is stars Ben Affleck as Batman, and Henry Cabell as Clark Kent/superman.
That sounds nice.  Is there a plot to the movie?  If its got Ben Affleck in it, then it must be nice.
Batman feels that Superman has too much power and needs to be stop before he turns on the humans.
Woah, that sounds crazy.  Does Batman have to use like a krytonite suit?
He uses some kind of special suit that sort of evens the playing field.
Ahaha.. that's funny.  Hmm.  Does Superman act like Batman is boring?
No, he actually is able to fight him pretty well. One of the best parts of the movie is it introduces wonder woman played by Gal Gadot.
Hmm.  That sounds crowded.
Does the movie sort of tie into the other Batman movies?
Yes, it is tied to man of steel, suicide squad, wonder woman, and justice league.
Oh, ok.  I guess there is a special series involved with those movies?
Yes, it is pretty dark. Very moody.
Does the movies waiver on the side of Batman over Superman or do they try to keep it favorably balanced?
Is seems like it's pretty balanced, Lex Luther is trying to cause trouble, and eventually a bigger villain appears that they have to fight together.
Ha, that'd be a great interaction.  Lex Luther and Batman.  Does Superman get jealous?
Batman find some crap tonight, and that helps able to fight him better.
Lol, thats cool.
Ha ha, that is supposed to say kryptonite.
Oh, that makes more sense.
Pff.. well the movie sounds great.  I hope to catch it on the television or somewhere..
At the end the real bad entity, ends up killing superman, but not before they are able to defeat it.
Wow, that's a bummer and surprising.
Hmm, ok.
When was it made?
At the end, it shows his grave, or coughing, and things are levitating off the top of it, so I have a feeling he'll be back.
I was gonna say (Superman doesn't ever die :/)
All in all it's a pretty good movie even though the critics didn't like it very much.
Ahright, well thats been good.  I liked the information and the talk and hope to see it sometime!
It looks like we're done, have a good day.
